				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For the term in economics, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internationalization" title="Internationalization">Internationalization</a>.  For <a href="Microsoft_Windows.html" title="Microsoft Windows">Windows</a>-specified term, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multilingual_User_Interface" title="Multilingual User Interface">Multilingual User Interface</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Localization_(disambiguation)" title="Localization (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Localization (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">"Multilingual software" redirects here. For software that is written in multiple programming languages, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polyglot_(computing)" title="Polyglot (computing)">Polyglot (computing)</a>.</div>
